			<div id="body-content">

			<h1 class="entry-title">Trope or fact? Technology creates more jobs than it destroys</h1>

					

				

				<h2 class="subhead">Will automation beget a jobless wasteland or more stimulating, creative employment? That's up for debate.</h2>

			
			

			<div class="entry-meta">				

				
					<span class="meta-sep">by</span> 	

					
						<span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" rel="author" href="http://radar.oreilly.com/jims" title="View all posts by Jim Stogdill">

